  "text": "For decades, Da-Cheng-Qi decoction (DCQD) has been widely used to treat SAP effectively in clinical settings in China. DCQD, a special type of treatment for selective gut decontamination [CITATION_1] , is composed of Rheum palmatum L. However, the molecular mechanisms of the systemic inflammatory response on the JAK2/STAT3 signaling pathway in SAP are not well understood.",
